Mixed martial arts: The light-heavyweight fighter Lyoto Machida defeats Ryan Bader on UFC on Fox: Shogun vs. Vera, earning a rematch with the current champion in the division, Jon Jones. (ESPN)Brazil football club Corinthians wins the 2012 FIFA Club World Cup, after a 1–0 win over Chelsea in the final. Paolo Guerrero scored the only goal of the game in Yokohama, Japan. Brazilian player Cássio Ramos is named as MVP of the tournament. (ESPN) (FIFA)